1
00:00:00,133 --> 00:00:01,365
Wait...

2
00:00:01,365 --> 00:00:03,200
Don't go!

3
00:00:06,866 --> 00:00:08,533
I love you.

4
00:00:12,100 --> 00:00:14,132
Kiyoi, wait!

5
00:00:14,132 --> 00:00:15,265
Wait!

6
00:00:15,265 --> 00:00:16,565
What?

7
00:00:16,565 --> 00:00:18,432
It's n-n-not what you think.

8
00:00:18,432 --> 00:00:20,293
What the hell is it with you?!

9
00:00:21,033 --> 00:00:23,333
I told you I don't care anymore.

10
00:00:23,933 --> 00:00:25,433
See you.

11
00:00:27,633 --> 00:00:30,666
He meant that goodbye.

12
00:00:31,066 --> 00:00:32,900
This time...

13
00:00:34,300 --> 00:00:37,266
it's over between us.

14
00:00:38,366 --> 00:00:40,466
Am I not good enough?

15
00:00:42,300 --> 00:00:45,000
The person you loved...

16
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:47,100
It was Kiyoi-kun, wasn't it?

17
00:00:49,966 --> 00:00:50,832
Yes.

18
00:00:50,832 --> 00:00:53,033
What is it about him...

19
00:00:53,033 --> 00:00:55,266
that you love?

20
00:00:55,800 --> 00:00:57,900
I can't explain it.

21
00:01:02,233 --> 00:01:03,933
Goodbye...

22
00:01:04,900 --> 00:01:06,433
Hira.

