00:01:40,166 --> 00:01:43,900
Will you hear my story, everyone?

35
00:01:43,900 --> 00:01:46,300
- Of course.
- Kiyoi! Kiyoi! Kiyoi!

36
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:48,573
You come in from there and say your lines.

