00:01:48,573 --> 00:01:50,165
I'm sorry.

38
00:01:50,165 --> 00:01:52,365
- Concentrate.
- Right.

39
00:01:52,365 --> 00:01:54,433
Ready... Start.

40
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:58,899
Will you hear my story, everyone?

41
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:01,533
- Of course.
- Of course, we will.

42
00:02:01,533 --> 00:02:04,865
- Thank you.
- Stop, stop, stop.

43
00:02:04,865 --> 00:02:06,299
Let's take a break.

44
00:02:06,299 --> 00:02:07,699
You've lost concentration.

45
00:02:07,699 --> 00:02:10,099
Take a break and review your lines.

46
00:02:10,099 --> 00:02:12,933
We'll pick up where we left off.

47
00:02:12,933 --> 00:02:14,800
Okay.

48
00:02:16,700 --> 00:02:18,865
Thanks for coming. How is the fever?

49
00:02:18,866 --> 00:02:21,532
- I'm fine now.
- Thanks.

50
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,499
Are you free tomorrow?

51
00:02:23,499 --> 00:02:28,032
One of my staff is... taking time off tomorrow.

52
00:02:28,032 --> 00:02:29,365
- Is that so?
- If you don't mind,

53
00:02:29,366 --> 00:02:31,400
can you help us out?

54
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,232
I probably can.

55
00:02:32,233 --> 00:02:33,199
- Can you really?
- Yes.

56
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:35,099
That would be a huge help. Thank you.

57
00:02:35,099 --> 00:02:37,933
- Want to watch?
- Yes.

58
00:02:55,133 --> 00:02:56,733
Kiyoi-kun...

59
00:02:58,466 --> 00:03:00,033
I...

60
00:03:00,966 --> 00:03:03,066
told Hira I love him.

61
00:03:07,100 --> 00:03:09,332
It's none of my business...

62
00:03:09,332 --> 00:03:12,833
If the two of you... hook up.

63
00:03:16,066 --> 00:03:19,100
Hira is... really...

64
00:03:19,100 --> 00:03:23,133
mean... and indecisive,

65
00:03:23,133 --> 00:03:25,799
but he can be oddly stubborn.

66
00:03:25,799 --> 00:03:27,800
Really selfish, right?

67
00:03:33,300 --> 00:03:35,466
You look disgusted.

68
00:03:36,366 --> 00:03:37,699
What?

69
00:03:37,699 --> 00:03:40,166
You say you don't care,

70
00:03:40,166 --> 00:03:43,266
but you get upset when you hear me badmouth him.

71
00:03:47,566 --> 00:03:49,066
Hira...

72
00:03:50,066 --> 00:03:53,033
said he only took one person's photo...

73
00:03:53,033 --> 00:03:56,000
in his entire life.

74
00:03:56,866 --> 00:03:59,800
He said it was a very beautiful person.

75
00:04:00,666 --> 00:04:02,900
He said he loves that person...

76
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,633
without any reason.

77
00:04:09,166 --> 00:04:11,400
What's your point?

78
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,966
I want the person I love...

79
00:04:18,233 --> 00:04:20,700
to be happy.

80
00:04:23,266 --> 00:04:26,833
That's... all.

81
00:04:47,566 --> 00:04:49,466
Hello?

82
00:05:00,733 --> 00:05:04,133
I'm so sorry about this! You're a real lifesaver.

83
00:05:04,133 --> 00:05:06,965
Anything I can do to help.

84
00:05:06,965 --> 00:05:08,799
Kazuki was supposed to help us today,

85
00:05:08,799 --> 00:05:11,533
but something suddenly came up.

86
00:05:12,033 --> 00:05:14,333
He said you could fill in.

87
00:05:16,133 --> 00:05:17,499
Koyama did?

88
00:05:17,499 --> 00:05:20,266
He said you're perfect for the job.

89
00:05:20,266 --> 00:05:21,800
Here.

90
00:05:23,133 --> 00:05:24,833
Okay.

91
00:05:24,833 --> 00:05:26,900
I'm counting on you!

92
00:05:29,300 --> 00:05:32,300
What was Koyama thinking?

93
00:05:32,966 --> 00:05:34,099
I think I know.

94
00:05:34,099 --> 00:05:35,733
I found myself

95
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:39,333
following her with my eyes...

96
00:05:41,566 --> 00:05:43,166
I love you.

97
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,533
I can't help it!

98
00:05:47,533 --> 00:05:49,500
I love you!

99
00:05:50,766 --> 00:05:54,033
Those were words he would never say to me.

100
00:06:01,700 --> 00:06:05,066
I wish I could spend the rest of my life

101
00:06:05,066 --> 00:06:08,533
being the light shining on Kiyoi.

102
00:06:11,930 --> 00:06:16,099
- Where do those go?
- Rehearsal room.

103
00:06:16,099 --> 00:06:18,499
I'll do it.

104
00:06:18,499 --> 00:06:21,132
Thanks. But it's a lot...

105
00:06:21,132 --> 00:06:23,832
You there... Hira-kun, was it?

106
00:06:23,832 --> 00:06:25,165
Help him, please.

107
00:06:25,166 --> 00:06:28,100
Those come here!

108
00:06:38,233 --> 00:06:40,100
Okay...

109
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:42,166
Put them here for now.

110
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:46,100
Put that down.

111
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:50,100
Stack them... over there.

112
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:51,665
Thanks.

113
00:06:51,665 --> 00:06:53,766
- Okay.
- Okay.

114
00:07:13,500 --> 00:07:15,933
- Hey!
- Y-Yes?

115
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:19,666
Why are you coming around me again?

116
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:24,333
W-Well...

117
00:07:25,300 --> 00:07:27,566
The words won't come out.

118
00:07:27,566 --> 00:07:29,700
What do I tell him?

119
00:07:30,666 --> 00:07:31,932
Forget it.

120
00:07:31,932 --> 00:07:33,633
Why don't you go home?

121
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,899
Uh-Uh-Uh, I...

122
00:07:36,899 --> 00:07:38,933
You're so damn annoying!

123
00:07:47,433 --> 00:07:49,233
Are you okay?

124
00:07:57,700 --> 00:07:59,100
What?

125
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,700
Hey...

126
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,966
You...

127
00:08:42,900 --> 00:08:44,833
S-Sorry.

128
00:08:44,833 --> 00:08:46,533
What?

129
00:08:46,533 --> 00:08:48,866
I'm sorry.

130
00:08:49,333 --> 00:08:51,266
Something came over me.

131
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:54,300
Came over you?

132
00:08:54,966 --> 00:08:57,933
I don't know

133
00:08:57,933 --> 00:09:00,233
why I did that to you...

134
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,266
What am I to you?

135
00:09:05,433 --> 00:09:07,866
The person I love most in the world.

136
00:09:08,566 --> 00:09:11,400
Are you saying you want to hook up?

137
00:09:11,866 --> 00:09:13,165
No.

138
00:09:13,165 --> 00:09:15,633
- Why not?
- Because you're the king.

139
00:09:16,366 --> 00:09:19,166
Because I am your servant.

140
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,633
Oh... So that's it.

141
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:28,733
I get it now.

142
00:09:28,733 --> 00:09:30,200
What?

143
00:09:31,066 --> 00:09:32,566
You...

144
00:09:33,066 --> 00:09:36,246
do things like this with someone who isn't even your boyfriend?

145
00:09:37,733 --> 00:09:42,566
I'm s-s-sorry...

146
00:09:43,633 --> 00:09:46,133
I won't do it again.

147
00:09:46,133 --> 00:09:48,600
Don't come around me anymore.

148
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:51,933
I don't care if you chase your ideal of me...

149
00:09:51,933 --> 00:09:54,933
but leave the real me alone!

150
00:09:56,066 --> 00:09:57,866
I don't think...

151
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:01,500
you'll ever understand my feelings.

152
00:10:02,300 --> 00:10:04,200
You're right.

153
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,032
Someone like me...

154
00:10:08,032 --> 00:10:10,600
can't understand how you feel, Kiyoi.

155
00:10:11,766 --> 00:10:13,566
I guess.

156
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:17,466
I don't understand your feelings, either.

157
00:10:18,233 --> 00:10:20,132
- Wait.
- Let go of me!

158
00:10:20,133 --> 00:10:21,299
I don't want to!

159
00:10:21,299 --> 00:10:24,065
Because this might be the last time!

160
00:10:24,065 --> 00:10:26,166
Dammit, you!

161
00:10:27,133 --> 00:10:29,366
Have you...

162
00:10:29,366 --> 00:10:32,300
even once considered that I love you?

163
00:10:36,566 --> 00:10:39,300
Th-Th-That's...

164
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:42,533
not possible.

165
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:59,133
I received many messages from Hira.

166
00:10:59,133 --> 00:11:00,865
Every one of them an apology.

167
00:11:00,865 --> 00:11:03,633
Not one showed he understood.

168
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:07,299
I believed that if I told him how I felt,

169
00:11:07,299 --> 00:11:09,800
we could be together.

170
00:11:09,800 --> 00:11:13,666
He probably doesn't think that I confessed my feelings to him.

171
00:11:13,666 --> 00:11:15,466
So be it.

172
00:11:15,466 --> 00:11:18,000
I'll just forget about it.

173
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,165
What kind of man was I?

174
00:11:20,165 --> 00:11:22,465
- I don't remember!
- Even though I wasn't in demand,

175
00:11:22,465 --> 00:11:27,133
rehearsals and auditions kept me busy.

176
00:11:27,133 --> 00:11:29,100
I was thankful for that.

177
00:11:36,766 --> 00:11:38,333
[Hira Voicemail]

178
00:11:38,333 --> 00:11:41,566
[Hira]

179
00:11:45,766 --> 00:11:47,866
I'm so, so sorry.

180
00:11:47,866 --> 00:11:50,199
I know I'm annoying you,

181
00:11:50,199 --> 00:11:53,465
so this will be the last time I contact you.

182
00:11:53,465 --> 00:11:57,300
Tonight... at the place where you first saved me,

183
00:11:57,300 --> 00:12:02,100
I will dedicate the night to my love for you.

184
00:12:02,666 --> 00:12:06,833
Today will be the last time I will think about you.

185
00:12:12,233 --> 00:12:13,900
I'm going to...

186
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,766
put an end to these feelings, too.

187
00:12:19,033 --> 00:12:20,533
Kiyoi-kun...

188
00:12:21,366 --> 00:12:24,099
After we're done, I'm meeting a show producer for dinner.

189
00:12:24,099 --> 00:12:26,865
- Do you want to come?
- We're resuming rehearsal!

190
00:12:26,865 --> 00:12:29,266
- Okay!
- Okay!

191
00:12:29,266 --> 00:12:32,566
We're going to be running late today.

192
00:12:32,566 --> 00:12:34,632
What? I have plans!

193
00:12:34,632 --> 00:12:36,965
Make this the priority. Please.

194
00:12:36,965 --> 00:12:39,566
That's not what the schedule said.

195
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:53,366
Kiyoi didn't come.

196
00:12:53,366 --> 00:12:55,466
Of course, he wouldn't.

197
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:59,700
This is... the reality.

198
00:14:39,366 --> 00:14:41,566
I wonder how the world appears...

199
00:14:43,700 --> 00:14:46,466
through Kiyoi's eyes.

200
00:14:50,666 --> 00:14:53,733
I'll move on to a new morning.

201
00:14:53,733 --> 00:14:56,100
And after that, I'll forget...

202
00:14:56,100 --> 00:14:58,180
the love...

203
00:14:58,610 --> 00:15:00,700
of my life.

204
00:15:03,866 --> 00:15:05,466
Kiyo...!

205
00:15:07,066 --> 00:15:09,033
Wait!

206
00:15:09,033 --> 00:15:10,432
I don't want to forget.

207
00:15:10,432 --> 00:15:12,373
I don't want it to be a memory.

208
00:15:12,373 --> 00:15:15,400
I know I'm being creepy,

209
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,000
but...

210
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,466
I can't lie about my feelings.

211
00:15:19,466 --> 00:15:21,899
Kiyoi is who I yearn for.

212
00:15:21,899 --> 00:15:23,532
He's self-centered and willful...

213
00:15:23,532 --> 00:15:24,950
That's why...

214
00:15:24,950 --> 00:15:28,030
he was my savior.

215
00:15:28,433 --> 00:15:30,099
Everything Kiyoi was...

216
00:15:30,099 --> 00:15:32,600
and everything Kiyoi will be...

217
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:35,066
I want to embrace it all.

218
00:15:36,233 --> 00:15:37,632
Let go of me!

219
00:15:37,632 --> 00:15:40,166
I love you, Kiyoi!

220
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:44,200
I really did intend to end it today!

221
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,832
But...

222
00:15:45,832 --> 00:15:47,799
then you...

223
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:50,499
Stop messaging and calling me!

224
00:15:50,499 --> 00:15:52,300
I'm sorry...

225
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:54,133
I'm sorry!

226
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,400
But I love you!

227
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:59,399
I want to forget you...

228
00:15:59,399 --> 00:16:02,020
but I can't when you shove yourself

229
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:04,560
into my life!

230
00:16:07,033 --> 00:16:10,166
I'm not the "King." Screw you!

231
00:16:11,466 --> 00:16:13,465
That's not what I am.

232
00:16:13,465 --> 00:16:15,500
I'm an ordinary guy.

233
00:16:18,166 --> 00:16:20,966
I want to be with the person I love.

234
00:16:20,966 --> 00:16:22,866
I want to touch him...

235
00:16:22,866 --> 00:16:25,200
I'm just an ordinary guy.

236
00:16:28,866 --> 00:16:30,766
Do you have someone...

237
00:16:33,533 --> 00:16:34,800
you love, Kiyoi?

238
00:16:34,800 --> 00:16:36,265
It's you!

239
00:16:36,265 --> 00:16:38,966
Stupid, how many times are you going to make me say it?

240
00:16:43,900 --> 00:16:45,700
Really?

241
00:16:45,700 --> 00:16:48,400
I wouldn't lie about something like this.

242
00:16:49,766 --> 00:16:53,766
I kissed you... on graduation day, didn't I?!

243
00:16:55,466 --> 00:16:56,933
But you...

244
00:16:58,266 --> 00:17:01,233
You didn't even come after me...

245
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,733
even though you kept saying how much you love me...

246
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:08,533
I couldn't understand!

247
00:17:12,633 --> 00:17:14,766
Why would you...

248
00:17:15,866 --> 00:17:17,399
love someone like me?

249
00:17:17,399 --> 00:17:19,833
I wish I knew!

250
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:23,733
I really don't know...

251
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:28,200
You're the one who told me you loved me first.

252
00:17:32,766 --> 00:17:34,966
You gave me that look...

253
00:17:37,766 --> 00:17:39,600
You even kissed me.

254
00:17:40,666 --> 00:17:42,533
But then...

255
00:17:43,433 --> 00:17:46,666
you changed your number.

256
00:17:46,666 --> 00:17:49,166
Do you know how that made me feel?!

257
00:17:55,866 --> 00:17:57,566
Kiyoi.

258
00:18:07,966 --> 00:18:09,465
Screw you, Hira!

259
00:18:09,465 --> 00:18:11,633
Go to hell!

260
00:18:16,433 --> 00:18:18,100
I...

261
00:18:18,766 --> 00:18:21,766
love you so much, Kiyoi, that it drives me crazy!

262
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:26,300
I think of you like a god.

263
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:30,766
I never thought I could have you.

264
00:18:32,600 --> 00:18:34,500
I'm...

265
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:39,066
not a god!

266
00:18:59,100 --> 00:19:00,966
Kiyoi...

267
00:19:06,133 --> 00:19:07,700
Can I...

268
00:19:09,533 --> 00:19:12,233
touch you, Kiyoi?

269
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,833
Not if it's the same way...

270
00:19:23,166 --> 00:19:24,633
you did before.

271
00:19:58,533 --> 00:20:00,233
Kiyoi...

272
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,933
I love you.

